KapitanLetters

Program for creating wordlists for bruteforce attacks. From a single word you can create a mix of its own with capital letters and even change certain vocals to numbers.

Usage: python Kapitan.py -w word_to_modify

-h --help - help options

-w --word - write here the word to modify

-n --notshow - do not show the words in command line

-s --save - specify a path/name to save the output in a file

-a - change all a for 4

-e - change all e for 5

-i - change all i for 1

-o - change all o for 0

Examples:

python Kapitan.py -w test -n -s pass.txt

python Kapitan.py --word test -e

python Kapitan.py -h
